{"tid":1387334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夢遊嘅小朋友，有多位哥哥想幫你地，真係唔好怕羞","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T20:01:43.000Z","uid":288186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"387bffc5e501fe6a4b75e6ab21abf98379471c97","tid":1387334,"uid":288186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4fSwff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4fSwff.png&h=f56ae81e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VyeLRfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVyeLRfq.png&h=544ae5e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56c53693883a46c26db4680c3ccddae964fae384","tid":1387334,"uid":144483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T20:01:43.000Z","msg":"謝你地呀<br />\n但求下你地多啲買gear買gear買gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實小朋友唔係個個都有嚴重經濟問題<br />\n我地已經唔介意食煙 擋子彈<br />\n又點會介意食小一兩餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心好多謝你地<br />\n但一餐可以平平地自己解決到<br />\ngear就真係好貴 講緊下下幾百起跳。。有啲負擔唔起<br />\n我唔想再見到有手足乜都冇就衝上最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白你地真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地 幫手買gear<br />\n多個眼罩頭盔豬咀 就少個人受傷被捕呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個真係最幫到手<br />\n買完找去現場 睇下邊個小朋友冇裝就塞比佢最岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你<br />\n<br />\n以下係需要既物資 <br />\n請幫手傳開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭盔：攀岩頭盔、電單車頭盔<br />\n<br />\n眼罩：3m GG2891S（唔戴眼鏡）<br />\n3m 2890s<br />\nSellstrom s80225/6<br />\nBolle 40100<br />\nBolle superblast 40926<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴：6200/6300 6500 7500<br />\n濾罐：60926 60921 60923 60925 60928<br />\n<br />\n手臂：冰袖（需配搭保鮮紙）<br />\n濕水棉質護手<br />\n長袖衫<br />\n<br />\n手套：電單車手套<br />\n<br />\n腳：護脛"}]}